<p>And Georgia Harrison enjoyed a heart-racing exercise of a different kind in a throwback video with Olympian Ashley Mckenzie on Sunday, which showed her practising her judo moves last year.</p>

<p>The reality star, 25, grimaced as she tried out the complex judo move which saw her flip the Judoka, 31, on his back, wrapped her leg around his neck and held him in an arm lock after he pin her down during their match last year.</p>

<p>Wow! Love Island's Georgia Harrison grimaced as she pulled off a complex judo move with Olympian Ashley Mckenzie ahead of first fight in a throwback video she shared on Sunday</p>

<p>Georgia showed off her toned figure in a black crop top and gym leggings that had a zebra print on the the sides. </p>

